00/david-villa?season=2013 |title=David Villa 2013/14 |publisher=Soccernet.espn.go.com |date= |accessdate=23 June 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140619150043/http://www.espnfc.com/player/28600/david-villa?season=2013 |archivedate=19 June 2014}}</ref>\n|3||2||3||1||6||3||{{#expr:3/6 round 2}}\n|-\n|2017\u201318<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espnfc.com/player/28600/david-villa?season=2017 |title=David Villa 2017/18 |publisher=Soccernet.espn.go.com |date= |accessdate=2 September 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903035042/http://www.espnfc.com/player/28600/david-villa?season=2017 |archivedate=3 September 2017}}</ref>\n|0||0||1||0||1||0||{{#expr:0/1 round 2}}\n|- style=\"background:beige\"\n!colspan=\"2\"|Career Total<ref>{{cite web| title = Jugadores \u2013 Real Federaci\u00f3n Espa\u00f1ola de F\u00fatbol| url = http://www.rfef.es/index.jsp?nodo=41&jugador=15| publisher = RFEF| accessdate = 13 September 2009| language = Spanish| url-status=dead| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091011175330/http://www.rfef.es/index.jsp?nodo=41&jugador=15| archivedate = 11 October 2009| df = dmy-all}}</ref><ref>HISTORIA DEL F\u00daTBOL ESPA\u00d1OL, SELECCIONES ESPA\u00d1OLAS {{in lang|es}} {{ISBN|978-84-8229-123-9}}</ref>\n!39||19||59||40||98||59||{{#expr:59/98 round 2}}\n|}\n\n'''Note''': ''Each season is September \u2013 August''\n\n==Honours==\n<ref name=\"SW\">{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/david-villa-sanchez/338/|title=David Villa|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=4 September 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904154724/http://us.soccerway.com/players/david-villa-sanchez/338/|archivedate=4 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=David Villa, Club info & Prize List|publisher=Eurosport|url=http://www.eurosport.com/football/david-villa_prs32411/person.shtml|accessdate=4 September 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904154144/http